This new development offers an unparalleled luxury lifestyle on the Costa del Sol. Located in the heart of prestigious Los Flamingos, just 5 minutes from the beach, this collection of 11 townhouses represents comfort and exclusivity.&#13;
&#13;
All homes feature:&#13;
&#13;
 	Private garden.&#13;
 	Private pool.&#13;
 	Private parking.&#13;
 	Spacious terraces.&#13;
 	Solarium.&#13;
&#13;
This project has been designed with maximum comfort, functionality, energy efficiency, and exceptional finishes in mind, including, among many other features:&#13;
&#13;
 	Air conditioning (hot/cold).&#13;
 	Underfloor heating throughout the house.&#13;
 	Advanced home automation.&#13;
&#13;
Nestled in the heart of Los Flamingos Golf course, surrounded by nature and tranquillity, while Estepona town centre is less than 10 minutes away. It also boasts excellent connections to Marbella, Sotogrande, and the airports of Málaga, Jerez, and Gibraltar.&#13;
&#13;
These home are the ideal choice for those seeking a luxury lifestyle in an exclusive setting.&#13;
&#13;
The remainuing homes (as of 22,07.2025) range from 1,015,000€ to 1,160,000€ plus purchase costs. The project has favourable payment terms with delivery in the middle of 2027.

Last 2 homes in an entirely unique concept with emphasis on cutting edge design and adhering to the absolute luxury appeal demanded by the discerning client&#13;
&#13;
Set in its own secure and landscaped gardens. the villas offers the ultimate in home automation, which provides homeowners security, comfort. convenience and energy efficiency by allowing them to control smart devices. often by a smart home app on their smartphone or another networked device.&#13;
&#13;
The ground floor is an open-plan design with large from floor to ceiling windows. which allows the natural flow of light to enter the property from its southeast-facing view.&#13;
&#13;
The villas have been designed with the climate in mind. with large outside terraced living space on the ground floor, large balconies attached to each of the 3 bedrooms on the first floor, and a 63m2 rooftop terrace which takes full advantage of the stunning panoramic views.&#13;
&#13;
In the basement strategically placed windows allow for abundant light and during construction, the buyer can alter the room sizes according to their needs. The current basement plans are for 2 bedrooms and one larger cinema room but one of the bedrooms could be replaced with a larger cinema/playroom. Each home as its own swimming pool which seamlessly connects to the villa allowing the blue reflection to shimmer through this property.&#13;
&#13;
A modern-style glass lift stands out. The interior is a lesson of perfection that make the villas one of the best properties in the area of  La Quinta which straddles Marbella and Benahavis.&#13;
&#13;
As of 22nd July 2025, there are two homes left:&#13;
&#13;
House 1 at 1,490,000€ plus purchase costs&#13;
&#13;
House 4 at 1,690,000€ plus purchase costs

