The last home in a key-ready development of 15 luxury villas that sit in a beautiful part of La Cala Golf.&#13;
&#13;
The homes are situated close to the club house of La Cala Golf Resort, and only 10 minutes from the beaches between La Cala de Mijas and Fuengirola.&#13;
&#13;
The luxury homes are finished to the highest standards using the finest quality materials, avant-garde design, neutral colours and large spaces. Floor-to-ceiling windows create a light filled home, crowned with a large solarium that covers the entire upper part of each villa.&#13;
&#13;
The lower level/basements of all the villas can be adapted to the requirements of the owner and set up as a leisure room, gym or spa, or even the two additional bedrooms.&#13;
&#13;
Each property has more than 300 m² built area, a private infinity pool, parking for two vehicles, and several terraces and a private garden. There are two remaining villas to choose from:-&#13;
&#13;
Villa 11 - 1,150,000 € &#13;
