Last 3 homes all price 575,000€ + VAT which is excellent value for a 4 bedroom detached property, with a private pool, on the Costa del Sol.&#13;
&#13;
Located in the prestigious Guarda Il Mare urbanisation, this boutique project offers 12 luxurious villas designed for modern living. The beach (with chiringuitos), a cafe/bar, a small supermarket and bus stops with busses heading towards La Duquesa, Estepona and Sotogrande are all within easy walking distance.&#13;
&#13;
Each home offers a spacious basement with garage and private cinema, an open-plan living area with kitchen and garden access, and three bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms.  There is a fourth room on the upper floor which could be a single bedroom or office.&#13;
&#13;
Outdoors, you’ll enjoy a generous garden and private saltwater pool. The homes have been designed with minimal barriers between indoor and outdoor spaces.&#13;
&#13;
With A-rated energy certification, solar panels, and seamless indoor-outdoor integration, these homes combine comfort, sustainability, and elegance on the Costa del Sol.&#13;
&#13;
Each villa has 3 floors on a 380m2 plot. There will be 4 bedrooms, 4+1 bathrooms, 200m2 built, 16.55m2 of terrace, 225m2 of garden, a saltwater pool and an underground garage.&#13;
&#13;
