**Exceptional Investment Opportunity on Marbella’s Prestigious Golden Mile**&#13;
&#13;
A rare chance to acquire a prime development plot with an approved project and full license for the construction of a secure, gated community comprising seven luxury residences. This exclusive opportunity is situated beachside on Marbella's coveted Golden Mile — one of the most sought-after and prestigious addresses in Southern Europe.&#13;
&#13;
All planning permissions and documentation are fully in place, allowing for immediate commencement of development. The project is thoughtfully designed to meet the high demand for upscale, contemporary homes in this iconic location.&#13;
&#13;
Ideally located within easy walking distance of both the world-renowned Puerto Banús marina and the elegant Puente Romano resort, the site offers residents unrivalled access to Marbella’s finest dining, nightlife, shopping, and beach clubs. As one of the very last remaining beachside plots available for development south of the N-340, this offering presents both scarcity and exclusivity — key drivers of long-term value.&#13;
&#13;
The projected return on investment is an impressive 30%, making this a highly attractive prospect for discerning investors and developers looking to secure a foothold in one of Europe's most stable and high-performing real estate markets.

The last two homes in a collection of eight off-plan townhouses on the front line of Estepona Golf Course. Situated a 10-minute drive from the center of Estepona and 20 minutes from the famous Puerto Banus, the development is designed to offer tranquillity and privacy while providing easy access to a wealth of facilities and amenities.&#13;
&#13;
The complex is made up of eight 3-bedroom townhouses overlooking the fairways of Estepona Golf Course. Each townhouse is built on three floors, comprising on the ground level an entrance hall with a dressing room, a spacious and stylish open-plan living and dining area with an integrated modern kitchen, a bedroom and a bathroom. This level has access to the terraces, garden area and private swimming pool.&#13;
&#13;
The first floor consists of two bedroom suites, each with a private terrace and a dressing area in the main bedroom. Upstairs is a rooftop solarium with fantastic views, and on the lower level is a spacious multi-purpose basement. Both the basement and the solarium can be fully customised to your own preference, offering endless possibilities. In addition, each townhouse has an off-road parking on its driveway.&#13;
&#13;
With a sleek and functional design, soothing neutral palettes enhanced with natural elements such as light oak and marble, these homes are ideally suited for a dynamic lifestyle. The latest building techniques ensure maximum energy efficiency, complemented by photovoltaic panels that harness solar power. Every residence is delivered with the possibility of a high quality interior design project.&#13;
&#13;
The residences boast an ideal location, next to the clubhouse and emerald fairways of one of the best golf courses in the area, and within a short driving distance of numerous prestigious golfing venues, such as Finca Cortesin. Also nearby are international schools, shopping centers, restaurants, sports and wellness amenities, and the stunning golden sands of the Costa del Sol.&#13;
&#13;
Estimated completion date: December 2026&#13;
&#13;
Contemporary Style&#13;
Modern interior design, with a spacious open-plan layout, sleek aesthetics with functional, comfortable living areas&#13;
&#13;
Private Community&#13;
Boutique community of just eight homes each with a private pool, overlooking the fairways of Estepona Golf Course&#13;
&#13;
Prime Location&#13;
A wealth of facilities and amenities on the doorstep, from schools and commercial centres to gourmet restaurants and the vibrant old town&#13;
&#13;
Energy Efficiency&#13;
The latest building techniques ensure maximum energy efficiency, complemented by photovoltaic panels installed to harness solar power&#13;
&#13;
